TITLE:BAX SEO Features - Boost Your Search Rankings
DATE:12 July 2026
IMG:https://placehold.co/800x400/0f172a/ffffff?text=BAX+SEO
DESC:Learn how BAX automatically generates SEO-friendly meta tags, Open Graph, and Twitter Cards to boost your search rankings.
TAGS:bax seo meta-tags opengraph twitter-cards

H2:SEO Made Simple with BAX
P:BAX automatically generates all the SEO meta tags you need for better search engine rankings. No plugins, no extra configuration - just pure SEO magic built right in!

P:Search engines love well-structured HTML with proper meta tags. BAX takes care of all of this for you, so you can focus on creating great content.

HR:

H2:Auto-Generated Meta Tags
P:BAX automatically generates the following meta tags for every page:

H3:Title Tag
P:BAX uses the post/page title or falls back to SITE_TITLE from config.
P:<title>Your Post Title - Your Site Title</title>

H3:Description Meta
P:BAX uses the post/page description or falls back to SITE_DESCRIPTION.
P:<meta name="description" content="Your post description"/>

H3:Open Graph Tags (Facebook, LinkedIn)
P:BAX generates complete Open Graph tags for social sharing:
UL:
LI:og:type - website or article
LI:og:title - post/page title
LI:og:description - post/page description
LI:og:image - post/page image or default
LI:og:url - post/page URL
/UL:

CODE:< meta property="og:type" content="article">
CODE:< meta property="og:title" content="Your Post Title">
CODE:< meta property="og:description" content="Your description">
CODE:< meta property="og:image" content="https://example.com/image.jpg">

H3:Twitter Card Tags
P:BAX generates Twitter Card tags for better sharing on Twitter:
UL:
LI:twitter:card - summary_large_image
LI:twitter:title - post/page title
LI:twitter:description - post/page description
LI:twitter:image - post/page image or default
/UL:

CODE:< meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
CODE:< meta name="twitter:title" content="Your Post Title">
CODE:< meta name="twitter:description" content="Your description">
CODE:< meta name="twitter:image" content="https://example.com/image.jpg">

H3:Generator Meta
P:BAX includes a generator meta tag for branding:
CODE:< meta name="generator" content="BAX v1.0 - Static Site Generator by Axcora">

HR:

H2:Priority System
P:BAX uses a smart priority system for SEO metadata:

H3:Priority Order
OL:
LI:Post/Page specific (highest priority)
LI:Site-wide config (fallback)
LI:Default values (last resort)
/OL:

P:This means you can set global values in config.zet and override them for specific posts or pages.

H3:Example
CODE:# config.zet - Global values
CODE:SITE_TITLE:My Awesome Site
CODE:SITE_DESCRIPTION:This is my awesome static site
CODE:SITE_IMAGE:https://example.com/default-og.jpg

CODE:# data/post.zet - Override for this post
CODE:TITLE:My Special Post
CODE:DESC:This post has its own description
CODE:IMG:https://example.com/post-image.jpg

HR:

H2:Sitemap and Robots.txt
P:BAX automatically generates two essential SEO files:

H3:Sitemap.xml
P:BAX generates a sitemap.xml that includes:
UL:
LI:All blog posts
LI:All static pages
LI:Tag pages
LI:Index pages with pagination
LI:Last modified dates
LI:Change frequencies
LI:Priority levels
/UL:

CODE:< ?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
CODE:< urlset xmlns="http://www.sitemaps.org/schemas/sitemap/0.9">
CODE:    < url>
CODE:        < loc>https://mysite.com/< / loc>
CODE:        < lastmod>2026-07-15T13:30:00< / lastmod>
CODE:        < changefreq>daily< / changefreq>
CODE:        < priority>1.0< / priority>
CODE:    < / url>
CODE:< / urlset>

H3:Robots.txt
P:BAX generates robots.txt to guide search engine crawlers:
CODE:User-agent: *
CODE:Allow: /
CODE:Disallow: /pages/
CODE:Disallow: /tags/
CODE:Sitemap: https://mysite.com/sitemap.xml

HR:

H2:Best Practices for SEO with BAX

H3:1. Always Set Descriptions
P:Every post and page should have a description:
CODE:DESC:This is my post description

H3:2. Use Descriptive Titles
P:Make your titles descriptive and include keywords:
CODE:TITLE:How to Build Static Sites with BAX

H3:3. Add Tags
P:Tags help organize content and create tag pages:
CODE:TAGS:static-site bax tutorial

H3:4. Add Images
P:Images improve engagement and social sharing:
CODE:IMG:https://example.com/image.jpg

H3:5. Set Your Site URL
P:Always set SITE_URL in config.zet:
CODE:SITE_URL:https://mysite.com

HR:

